Welcome to Tez, a new payments app by Google! Tez is the best way to send money to friends, instantly receive payments directly to your bank account & pay the nearby café. And we’ve been working on some exciting new features to make Tez even better for you. Here’s what’s new and improved:

• Bug fixes and performance improvements

Welcome to Tez, a new payments app by Google! Tez is the best way to send money to friends, instantly receive payments directly to your bank account & pay the nearby café. And we’ve been working on some exciting new features to make Tez even better for you. Here’s what’s new and improved:

• Bug fixes and performance improvements

Welcome to Tez, a new payments app by Google! Tez is the best way to send money to friends, instantly receive payments directly to your bank account & pay the nearby café. And we’ve been working on some exciting new features to make Tez even better for you. Here’s what’s new and improved:

• Tuning app for bank performance
• Bug fixes and performance improvements

• Improved referrals flow
• More detailed error messages for adding a bank account or processing a payment
• Bug fixes and improved performance

• Ability to report an issue with a offer
• New status details for adding bank accounts

• Ability to report an issue with a offer
• New status details for adding bank accounts

• Search for businesses by name
• Added a section for suggested businesses
• Additional details so you can track the status of your payments
• Performance improvements and bug fixes

• Support for iPhone X and Face ID as additional security options
• Performance improvements and bug fixes
• Performance improvements and bug fixes

• Ability to pay bills such as DTH, electricity and utilities, and post-paid mobile bills; and get notifications when new bills arrive
• Performance improvements and bug fixes

• Chat with friends when making payments
• Performance improvements and bug fixes
• Performance improvements and bug fixes
• Performance improvements and bug fixes
• Performance improvements and bug fixes

• Theme your payments with sparks. They’re fun animations to make a payment extra special.
• Use Touch ID to unlock Tez
• Performance improvements and bug fixes
• Performance improvements and bug fixes.
• Performance improvements and bug fixes.
• Performance improvements and bug fixes.

• Improvements to conversation page
• Upgraded pay-to-account number feature

• Recharge your mobile phone
• Bug fixes and performance improvements
• Tez is now Google Pay. While our name has changed, all the features like direct-to-bank and rewards are here to stay
• Better support for new phone numbers

• New phone number series now supported in the app
• Improved suggested business groups in contacts screen
• Improved visual elements in the app for navigation
• Improved search experience
• Improved search experience for bill payments

• Send scratch cards to your friends on Google Pay
• Buy and sell Gold as little as ₹1 on Google Pay
• Users from select banks can get instant loans
• Improved experience for bill payment and recharge conversations
• Improved experience for transaction details
• Improvements in bank account registration flow
• UI fixes and stability improvements
• Improvements to conversation page with additional payment status details

This update addresses a bug which was affecting the network cellular detection for users on iOS 12.0.x.

Go ahead and use the app now to pay bills, recharge your mobiles, and pay online just like you used to. And keep sending us feedback so we can keep making the app better, one update at a time!

We've listened to your feedback and we've made several improvements to the payment experience.
As always, we are here to help! Do leave us a feedback, to help improve your mobile payment experience further.
